VulnAI Pro – AI OSINT Intelligence Platform

🚀 Overview
VulnAI Pro is an AI-powered OSINT and attack surface intelligence platform that performs passive reconnaissance and transforms raw data into actionable security insights.

🔍 Features
AI Risk Scoring Engine
Attack Surface Analysis
OSINT Aggregation (crt.sh, DNS, Wayback, Threat Intel)
Ethical Passive-Only Scanning

⚙️ Installation

bash
git clone https://github.com/namra0043/vulnai-pro
cd vulnai-pro
pip install -r requirements.txt


▶️ Run
python app.py

⚠️ Note
This is a prototype built for hackathon purposes. Some integrations (API keys, extended modules) are under development.

